    "long_instructions": "# Do This\r\n1. Create a function called `navigate_path` that moves the Painter forward until it can no longer move.\r\n    - Hint: Use the`while painter.can_move()` method to set a direction for the Painter.\r\n2. Use the `navigate_path()` function inside a loop to navigate through the Neighborhood.\r\n    - Hint: Remember to use the `turn_left()` and `turn_right()` functions as needed.\r\n3. Run your code and observe how the Painter collects paint and moves forward.\r\n",
